cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB port for S1U to 0 causes connection failures and prevents proper data transmission in the NG-U interface.

du.explanation_en: Setting the remote N port D to 0 causes port binding failures and disrupts F1 interface communication.
du.explanation_zh: 將遠端 N 端口 D 設定為 0 會導致端口綁定失敗，並干擾 F1 接口通信。
